                            <comment id="12414081" author="naka" created="Thu, 1 Jun 2006 00:20:14 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;There seems to exist subject  of treatment for tab ...&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1) &lt;br/&gt;
Should it be untabfied ?&lt;br/&gt;
2) &lt;br/&gt;
If it should be untabfied, what number is best for tab width ?&lt;br/&gt;
Tab width=8 is just a configuration in my development environment...&lt;/p&gt;

